Summary: Flying rod captured in sequence of photographs.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was traveling North on I-39 near Edgerton, WI and was taking a sequence of photos of an unusual looking cloud forming and later when I looked at the photos I noticed a white rod flying through one of the frames. (2nd photo) I've attached the before and after photos as well. Nothing real exciting but it's another piece of the puzzle.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Edgerton
This sighting has never been favorited.
